add a new modfier Reborn to Lava
The Volcano will Debuff the enemys with Lava Creation for 3.5 seconds, upon death enemys will spawn a Lava Spawn with their own stats
and 2 passive. Only 4 can be alive and they will last 70 seconds. Volcano will also do a Explosion after Volcanus stop Channeling for at
least 3 seconds, 50% of Volcano radius will be the Explosion dealing 50 plus 75% of inteillgence in magical damage and giving enemys
Soul Burn with all of its effect but also having 1.5 seconds duration reduce, Volcanus will gain 5 health for every Lava Spawn Created
at 50 health gain, increase volcanus health by 10% and health regeneration by 3.5, at 150 health gain, Volcano will have 8 base damage
bonus and increase Volcanus health regeneration Source by 30% and reduce the duration of healing source reduction by 25%. Max of 200
health gain and he lose all of them on death.

